    <briefdescription>
<para><bold> Class <computeroutput>ohmic</computeroutput> represents a symmetric ohmic bath x^2*exp(-x/x_c) density of states </bold> </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Purpose</title><para></para>
</simplesect>
<blockquote><para>This class contains the data structures for representing the density of states for an ohmic bath and includes a free parameter: the cutoff energy <formula id="182">$ \omega_c $</formula> and is adapted so the spectrum is antisymmetric (boson). </para>
</blockquote></para>
    </detaileddescription>
